data.description: Perfect Starter Home! Come tour this recently remodeled 3-4 bedroom home with spacious backyard! Step inside to a bright living room area that leads to an open concept Kitchen and dining area. Perfect for entertaining your guests. Backyard has a storage shed that has plumbing and electrical services.  Conveniently located minutes away from Highway 59. This home has so many features and wonderful things to offer. Schedule a showing today! You don’t want to miss this one.
